About this item

  • Fast Setup & Take DownThe Hydraulic system of pop up tents for adults makes it quick to set up the camping tent in 60 seconds and take it down in just 2 minutes. The pre-installed sturdy poles and lightweight structure make the assembly process simple and efficient, allowing you to fully enjoy the perfect outdoor vacation.
  • 2 in-1 Double Layer Camping Tent The double-layer instant pop-up dome tent eatures a unique adjustable design for the top canopy and includes a detachable outer tent and inner tent. As a whole, pop-up tents can be combined into a dual-layer structure for better wind resistance, and waterproofing. Tent cloth can be used as a sunshade, outer tent cloth, pavilion, awnindg, canopy, etc.
  • What You Get You will receive a 2-3 man tent, as well as 4 windproof ropes, 10 stainless steel stakes and a storage size. Inner tent size: 210*180*105cm, big enough for 2 adults or 4 children. Folding size: 78x 19 x18cm, you can easily pack the tent into a carry bag. Whether you are camping with family or friends, you can enjoy ample ground space to move around and store equipment.
  • Waterproof and Durable This camping tent features sturdy fiberglass poles to handle rugged terrain and seasons; The inner and outer tents are made of 190T polyester (waterproof index up to 3000 mm), double-layer structure, durable 210D Oxford rainproof cloth, rainproof and detachable outer tent canvas to ensure that the hiking tent can remain stable in any weather.
  • Good Ventilation The double-door design of the 2 man waterproof tent combines ventilation and windproofing, and the zipper design protects your privacy. Two mesh windows allow you to breathe fresh air, enjoy the beautiful scenery, and prevent mosquitoes from entering. Provide you with a more ventilated and comfortable living environment during your travel.
  • Wide Range of Use Whether for family outings, group adventures, or long-distance hiking, this 2 man pop up tent offers greater flexibility and convenience, making it an ideal choice for outdoor enthusiasts. This backpacking tent is suitable for family outings, friends gatherings, pets or equipment storage. One tent can meet multiple needs and unlock unlimited outdoor possibilities!

    How customer reviews and ratings work

    Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings, help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

    To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyses reviews to verify trustworthiness.
